Run on a machine which is running MT and MySQL.

Set the database, username, and password in src/settings.py

From inside the src directory, run the following command:

python manage.py runserver 8080

On JumpBox (you'll need to open port 8080 via iptables):

python manage.py runserver 0.0.0.0:8080

View default blog at:

http://localhost:8080/my_blog/index.html

Try out different styles (all template pages are WP sandbox-compatible):

http://localhost:8080/my_blog/app/select_style.html

